"title": "8116: discipleship, cost of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8116: discipleship, cost of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The denial of self-interests and desires, and a total commitment to do the will of God, even to the point of death.</p>\n<h2>The cost of discipleship involves a denial of self-interests and desires</h2>\n<h3>The cost involves self-denial</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:38\">MAT 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:27\">LUK 14:27</a></p>\n<h3>Self-denial means not living for oneself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:7\">ROM 14:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:15\">2CO 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:2\">1PE 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>The cost of discipleship is to be carefully considered</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:28-Luke14:32\">LUK 14:28–14:32</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The cost of discipleship means total commitment to the will of God</h2>\n<h3>Total surrender is required</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:33\">LUK 14:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:7-Phil3:8\">PHP 3:7–3:8</a></p>\n<h3>The security of the world is to be resisted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:19-Matt8:20\">MAT 8:19–8:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57-Luke9:58\">LUK 9:57–9:58</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ must have first priority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:59-Luke9:60\">LUK 9:59–9:60</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:21-Matt8:22\">MAT 8:21–8:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:21\">MAT 19:16–19:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:21\">MRK 10:17–10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:22\">LUK 18:18–18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">COL 1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ must come before family ties</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:61-Luke9:62\">LUK 9:61–9:62</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:37\">MAT 10:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26\">LUK 14:26</a></p>\n<h2>The cost of discipleship is constant</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The cost of discipleship includes persecution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:20\">JHN 15:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a></p>\n<h2>The cost of discipleship includes willingess to suffer and die for Jesus Christ's sake</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:38-Matt10:39\">MAT 10:38–10:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24-Matt16:25\">MAT 16:24–16:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34-Mark8:35\">MRK 8:34–8:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23-Luke9:24\">LUK 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:25\">JHN 12:25</a></p>",
